OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773342674
OL,3,CFormer police officer died on moving
OL,4,Cbus that hit pothole, friends say
OL,6,FThe friends of a former police
OL,7,Fofficer, who died after falling on a
OL,8,Fmoving bus, say the fall was caused by
OL,9,Fa pothole.
OL,11,FMarjorie Bramley, 90, from
OL,12,FNottinghamshire was on her way to a
OL,13,Fpharmacy when she fell while riding an
OL,14,FOn Demand bus in Carlton in November
OL,15,Flast year.
OL,17,FShe broke her back and died in
OL,18,Fhospital a week later - on 3 December
OL,19,Flast year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
