FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773342674
OL,3,CFormer police officer died on moving
OL,4,Cbus that hit pothole, friends say
OL,6,FFriends Mary and Gerald Cooper
OL,7,Freceived a call to say she was in
OL,8,Fhospital with serious injuries.
OL,10,FMary said: "We were told that she'd
OL,11,Ffallen on the bus. She'd stood up with
OL,12,Fher walker, then we understand the bus
OL,13,Fhit a pothole as it pulled into the
OL,14,Fbay - and that jolt loosened her grip
OL,15,Fand she fell backward onto a metal
OL,16,Fstep that was on the bus. That, we
OL,17,Funderstand broke her vertebrae."
OL,19,FMarjorie went from being an active 90-
OL,20,Fyear-old, to being immobile in
OL,21,Fhospital on palliative care.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773342674
OL,3,CFormer police officer died on moving
OL,4,Cbus that hit pothole, friends say
OL,6,FAn inquest recorded a verdict of
OL,7,Faccidental death, with injuries caused
OL,8,Fwhen Marjorie lost her balance on a
OL,9,Fmoving bus. Her friends believe
OL,10,Fpotholes caused that loss of balance.
OL,12,FMary described the state of the roads:
OL,13,F"I think you take your life in your
OL,14,Fown hands when you go out because
OL,15,Fyou're so busy concentrating how to
OL,16,Fzigzag around something. It's not a
OL,17,Fpleasure to drive, the roads just
OL,18,Fdon't seem fit for purpose."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773342674
OL,3,CFormer police officer died on moving
OL,4,Cbus that hit pothole, friends say
OL,6,FMarjorie has been described by her
OL,7,Ffriends as dignified, kind,
OL,8,Fcompassionate and with a "lovely sense
OL,9,Fof humour".
OL,11,FGerald said: "She made the most of her
OL,12,Flife. She didn't just sit back in her
OL,13,Fchair or lay in bed, she'd be up and
OL,14,Fabout and marching out."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773342674
OL,3,CFormer police officer died on moving
OL,4,Cbus that hit pothole, friends say
OL,6,FMary said: "I knew she had been a
OL,7,Fpolice lady. She joined the Royal Navy
OL,8,Fand she was one of the reserved Wrens
OL,9,Fwho walked across the Royal Albet Hall
OL,10,Fin front of the Queen and royal
OL,11,Ffamily, and I remember seeing this
OL,12,Fdignified military person."
OL,14,FITV News Central has contacted
OL,15,FNottinghamshire County Council, which
OL,16,Fruns the bus service and has
OL,17,Fresponsibility for the roads in the
OL,18,Fcounty.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
